Class Athlete

java.lang.Object
main.Purchasable
main.Athlete
public class Athlete extends Purchasable
This is the Athlete class which represents a single Athlete. The class extends Purchasable as Athletes can be bought and sold to make a Team.
Author:
Kush Desai, Yunu Cho
